      <title>兰德（Rand）作为南非政客辩论至关重要的预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/rand-gyrates-as-south-african-politicians-debate-crucial-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的兰特（Rand）融合了联盟政府的两个主要伙伴之间的谈判，旨在确保国家预算达成协议。]]></description>
